{"TopicId":203517,"ForumId":148,"TopicTitle":"Kerbonauts, we want to hear from you!","CreatedByName":"StarSlay3r","CreatedById":209403,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-06T16:00:00Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"StarSlay3r","CreatedById":209403,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-06T16:00:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-fileid=\u0022375\u0022 data-ratio=\u002252.33\u0022 data-unique=\u0022p7gwmkuus\u0022 style=\u0022width: 600px; height: auto;\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022KSP Logo FBTW.png\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/monthly_2021_07/514188615_KSPLogoFBTW.png.b2d13cf84cc9d332e53d093b90946128.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nWhether you\u0027re a Kerbonaut who\u0027s only been playing for a few weeks or for an entire decade, we want to hear from you!\u003Cbr\u003E\n\uFEFF\u003Cbr\u003E\nPlease complete this short KSP survey. \u25BA\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://bit.ly/kspsurvey1f\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022border:0px; color:#3397ff; font-size:16px; padding:0px; text-align:start; vertical-align:baseline\u0022 target=\u0022_blank\u0022\u003Ehttps://bit.ly/kspsurvey1f\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#181b34; color:#d5d8df; font-size:16px; text-align:start\u0022\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceman.Spiff","CreatedById":209133,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-06T16:40:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDone!\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nI\u2019m not sure what\u2019s changed but I haven\u2019t been getting notifications from these announcements.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:/\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-07-06T16:40:26Z\u0022 title=\u002207/06/2021 04:40  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 6, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Spaceman.Spiff\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-06T16:47:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224000540\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203517\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221625589603\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022209133\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spaceman.Spiff\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, Spaceman.Spiff said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m not sure what\u2019s changed but I haven\u2019t been getting notifications from these announcements.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBeen an issue for me for months as well. The issue appears to fall on deaf ears (much like these posts because of the lack of notifications \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E )\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-07-06T16:47:39Z\u0022 title=\u002207/06/2021 04:47  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 6, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by MechBFP\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spaceman.Spiff","CreatedById":209133,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-06T16:51:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224000544\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203517\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221625590041\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184845\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MechBFP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, MechBFP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBeen an issue for me for months as well. T\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame. I only now mentioned it because it seems to be a significant thing that they want people to see.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy guess is that the post is hidden and then revealed which \u201Cposts\u201D it, but not in the typical manner. This happened\u00A0with TOTM at one point.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-06T17:07:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappy to participate in the survey, I hope it helped!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:happy:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/happy.png\u0022 title=\u0022:happy:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Linky","CreatedById":208516,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-06T18:51:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wonder what this survey is for. As for the \u0022wish-list\u0022 I know what I want. Squad, can you quickly add bigger landing legs in 12.2?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Terminal Velocity","CreatedById":209328,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-06T18:53:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ndid the kurvey!! (I had to kerbalize\u00A0that sentence LOL)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dientus","CreatedById":209823,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-06T19:51:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDone and done.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Souptime","CreatedById":204451,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-06T20:40:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFinito!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FleshJeb","CreatedById":111640,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-06T21:18:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027ll know which one was mine.\u00A0(Even though I tried to be more constructive than vituperative.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LHACK4142","CreatedById":208897,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-06T21:33:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMOAR IVAs\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fragtzack","CreatedById":198037,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-06T22:40:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022The\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Eone\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Ething you want to see added to KSP2 ?\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat was a fracking tough question. Spent about 10 minutes trying to limit my response to one answer and I still failed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lewie","CreatedById":203745,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-07T01:38:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s good to see a company that CARES about their community like this!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-07-07T01:39:01Z\u0022 title=\u002207/07/2021 01:39  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 7, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Lewie\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ben J. Kerman","CreatedById":204948,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-07T02:53:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSubmitted it just now!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-07T03:30:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSubmitted\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-07T03:46:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224000762\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203517\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221625611212\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022198037\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022fragtzack\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, fragtzack said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022The\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Eone\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Ething you want to see added to KSP2 ?\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t remember any such question in that survey. At least, not about KSP\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E2\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/u\u003E; that question just said \u0027Kerbal Space Program\u0027. So, hopeless optimist that I am, that is exactly how I answered it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe only questions specifically about KSP 2 are whether you plan to buy it when released, and what would make you more likely to buy it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mattinoz","CreatedById":118580,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-07T04:23:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224000762\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203517\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221625611212\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022198037\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022fragtzack\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, fragtzack said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u0022The\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Eone\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Ething you want to see added to KSP2 ?\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat was a fracking tough question. Spent about 10 minutes trying to limit my response to one answer and I still failed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat was the easy one - \u0022what most excites you about KSP2\u0022 was too hard for me.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"zer0Kerbal","CreatedById":190933,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-07T06:01:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EMoar!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003Emy theme song for launches...\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#2c3e50;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:20px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003EThis (game) will never end because I want moar! Give me moar! give me moar! give me moar!\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/FFWVjdS1Kz4?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Missingno200","CreatedById":161623,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-07T06:35:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLovely poll.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you had a magic wand and could add any one thing to Kerbal Space Program, what would it be?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaximum optimization now that the final feature update is done. That, or the ability to set the inventories before launch, rather than going into the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E and doing it from there. Thats for KSP1, but should definitely be added to KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-07T09:25:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas somebody actually read the rules/disclaimer in the beginning?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, seriously?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Captain_Elson","CreatedById":208939,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-07T10:22:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve made my submission.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHope this can help in some way\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Caerfinon","CreatedById":207619,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-07T11:13:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid the survey, now back to \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u0022\u003Cspan\u003E \u003C/span\u003E\u003Cspan\u003EGoing to space going there can\u0027t wait gotta go. Space. Going.\u0022\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheEco","CreatedById":205909,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-07T11:33:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHonestly, the only thing I want for KSP2 is advanced habitation. Like, having difficulties where it would be Kerbals don\u0027t need to consume and then Kerbals need certain amounts of food, water, oxygen, exercise or gravity (for health) and entertainment. Also, more advanced interiors and Kerbal mechanics, like Kerbals needing to work on multiple systems to sustain the ship. Of course, these options would hopefully be optional. Also hire me KSP team because I have a fantastic idea for later gameplay!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-07-07T11:33:45Z\u0022 title=\u002207/07/2021 11:33  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 7, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by TheEco\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JB182","CreatedById":210976,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-07T12:54:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI did the survey!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-07T13:53:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224000901\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203517\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221625649904\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHas somebody actually read the rules/disclaimer in the beginning?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, seriously?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYa, the terms and conditions are pretty funny.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t put your secret life\u0027s work into the survey. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}